Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.13,0:00:16.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该不知道娜娜莉的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.39,0:00:17.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.68,0:00:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我答案
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.45,0:00:21.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀 真有你的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.50,0:00:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问 你不是哥哥吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:28.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 我不能对娜娜莉说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.11,0:00:31.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.11,0:00:34.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗洛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.87,0:00:42.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好 麻烦继续保持
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.60,0:00:45.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别忘了时间限制
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.38,0:00:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.51,0:00:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说 娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.68,0:00:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 果然是你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.04,0:00:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我必须装作不认识你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.86,0:00:56.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是必须的 希望你配合我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.78,0:01:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会去接你的 一定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.14,0:01:02.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以在此之前 在此之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.28,0:01:04.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你 娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.91,0:01:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问 您是否认错人了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:12.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 我只是一介学生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.81,0:01:17.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修 果然还没恢复记忆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.67,0:01:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.72,0:01:20.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该道歉的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.86,0:01:23.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说是朱雀重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.78,0:01:25.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一时心急便误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.48,0:01:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.29,0:01:28.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.25,0:01:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能和公主殿下说上话 是我的荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.01,0:01:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…能麻烦你把电话还回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.23,0:01:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,YES Your Highness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.19,0:01:40.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.55,0:01:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像让你误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,0:01:43.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.87,0:01:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的感觉确实很像哥哥 让我吃了一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.95,0:01:47.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.02,0:01:50.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 在11区再见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.57,0:01:53.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可轻视他们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.10,0:01:56.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论处于多么不利的境地 他毕竟是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:01:58.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会采取什么行动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.25,0:01:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.67,0:02:02.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这对得起「帝国之矛尖」这称号吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.98,0:02:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉总督有我陪同
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.60,0:02:07.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不劳你大驾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.15,0:02:08.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是ZERO…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.36,0:02:09.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉尔弗德卿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.04,0:02:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.85,0:02:14.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的ZERO不过是冒名顶替罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.64,0:02:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然惧怕一个假货
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.24,0:02:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不觉得对不起科奈莉娅公主殿下吗
