Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.31,0:02:23.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗伊德伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.78,0:02:26.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lancelot的部件调整花了不少功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:28.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.44,0:02:30.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久违了 罗伊德博士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.66,0:02:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 当了皇帝酱的直属嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.58,0:02:36.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放肆 竟如此称呼皇帝陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.44,0:02:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实 实在抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.54,0:02:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗伊德先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.28,0:02:41.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？有什么不对的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.92,0:02:43.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您一点都没变
