Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.69,0:04:55.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新总督的姓名和经历目前尚未公开
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:58.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题在于中华联邦总领事馆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:04:59.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.10,0:05:01.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由于没有官方发布
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:04.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有评论认为这可能只是高亥总领事的一人独断
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.27,0:05:08.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总领事在国内的立场可能会造成权力均势的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.00,0:05:12.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,11区的形势如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:14.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道？详情我也不大清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:17.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外面的世界怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朕从没出过这座城
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.78,0:05:25.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣上 这洛阳朱禁城才是世界的中心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.60,0:05:26.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.21,0:05:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去外面替圣上看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.05,0:05:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实 我今日是前来告辞的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.08,0:05:38.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朕好不容易才交到第一个朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.47,0:05:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.07,0:05:43.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是外子还在等我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.67,0:05:49.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新泻的物资接收似乎很顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:50.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.29,0:05:55.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 无法回到这总领事馆来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.34,0:05:56.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.16,0:06:00.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新总督是娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.32,0:06:02.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能战斗吗 和妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗？和娜娜莉？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.25,0:06:07.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是哪门子的玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.85,0:06:09.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么要置之不理吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.63,0:06:10.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不值一谈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.29,0:06:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去 娜娜莉就会像以前一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.58,0:06:15.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次沦为政治的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:18.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法行走 双目失明的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.84,0:06:20.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是打算视她作棋子用完便抛弃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是为了阻止这种事才开始行动的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.99,0:06:25.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色骑士团就是为此存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.81,0:06:27.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO是为娜娜莉而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.93,0:06:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道这是你的生存意义
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:32.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.45,0:06:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要创造一个娜娜莉能够幸福生活的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:38.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此一定要摧毁布里塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.23,0:06:42.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个叫V.V.的家伙 在布里塔尼亚本国吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:44.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:47.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是V.V.是你父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.60,0:06:50.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亚皇帝查尔斯的第一个同志
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.81,0:06:51.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同志？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.97,0:06:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两人曾经发过誓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:57.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弑杀神祗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.07,0:06:58.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是我们的契约
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:02.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 查尔斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.61,0:07:05.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不告诉娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.37,0:07:08.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO的真面目和Geass的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.39,0:07:10.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没那个必要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.36,0:07:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查尔斯 你还小呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.65,0:07:18.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是这样吗 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.26,0:07:26.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉总督呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.83,0:07:27.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在庭园里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:29.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算让她来舰桥…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.77,0:07:30.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没意义
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.48,0:07:33.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不见了？黑色骑士团？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.45,0:07:36.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我们也刚刚确认
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.00,0:07:38.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就和你们共享情报吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:43.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样各位就能明白 我国对布里塔尼亚没有敌意了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.22,0:07:45.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO也一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.72,0:07:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.19,0:07:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连同Knightmare都不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.87,0:07:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎是从地底阶层离去的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.52,0:07:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:54.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就不清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.26,0:07:56.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成 要把娜娜莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.04,0:07:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被摆了一道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.42,0:08:00.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要回击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.66,0:08:05.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色骑士团？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.11,0:08:09.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作战目的是俘虏新总督
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.08,0:08:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论发生什么事都绝不允许伤害她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.89,0:08:14.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到没 绝不允许
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.90,0:08:15.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:21.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么呢 玉城
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.58,0:08:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外行人 把陆军兵器弄上天又有何用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.46,0:08:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,张开Surface Flare也不是问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.96,0:08:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包围歼灭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.69,0:08:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤堂将军 之后就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.93,0:08:39.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 副司令你们也要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.68,0:08:46.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成 在这上面？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.57,0:08:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又有2架敌方Knightmare 落到本舰主翼上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.93,0:08:54.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,护卫舰上似乎也有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.44,0:08:55.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请将航空战力…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.78,0:08:59.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愚蠢的指挥官
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.42,0:09:02.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将航空战力集中到烟雾里这一手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:03.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就看破了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.39,0:09:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旗舰以外的就别凑热闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.19,0:09:13.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我们撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.00,0:09:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的空战部队也都派出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.87,0:09:17.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,护卫舰也展开炮击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.36,0:09:19.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是敌人集中攻击浮空装置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.75,0:09:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,展开护盾后难以瞄准…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.88,0:09:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不保护这里还要护卫舰做什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早知如此 就该把吉尔弗德卿也带来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.30,0:09:31.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东京租界的援军过来也要一小时左右
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.14,0:09:34.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是被Knightmare侵入怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.40,0:09:35.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁定被击坠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:37.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管这个 先确认幸存者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.41,0:09:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.09,0:09:45.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.72,0:09:53.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:10:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉 我这就去救你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.01,0:10:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}注：出自源义经连跳八船而逃的典故
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.01,0:10:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘技 八艘飞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.60,0:10:15.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算展开了护盾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.20,0:10:17.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦侵入还不是手到擒来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.56,0:10:19.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,航空战斗力看来也完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.67,0:10:22.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得意忘形会变成因幡白兔的（详见古事记）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.70,0:10:25.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦好啦 还是按基本的来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.78,0:10:29.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东京来的援军 太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:32.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 按方位而言是殿后部队
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.00,0:10:34.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还装有浮空组件？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.23,0:10:35.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Knightmare？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.33,0:10:39.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会 那机体是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.76,0:10:41.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 落幕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.22,0:10:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全机 功率正常
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.13,0:10:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,量产真令人愉快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.22,0:10:47.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.18,0:10:49.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把经费划在修奈泽尔殿下账上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.99,0:10:52.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么关系 他很快就会发觉的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.62,0:10:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你没跟他说？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.93,0:10:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能飞了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.19,0:11:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悟性还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.93,0:11:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 机体特性跟不上！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.27,0:11:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 之后拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.52,0:11:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉尔弗德那家伙 擅自行动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.70,0:11:10.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.16,0:11:13.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,功劳都被他抢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,条件都成熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.32,0:11:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下战局就逆转了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.00,0:11:22.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉
Comment: 0,0:00:02.96,0:00:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//-------------------TXTB---------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.48,0:11:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO侵入了舰内
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.18,0:11:33.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守卫在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.61,0:11:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉总督 是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.60,0:11:37.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上联系阿普森将军…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.94,0:11:42.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无人能阻止两人的重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.09,0:11:45.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.74,0:11:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于见到你了 终于
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:54.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里的是ZERO吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.59,0:11:57.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也要杀了我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.01,0:12:01.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像杀了克洛维斯皇兄和尤菲皇姐一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.58,0:12:05.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 能请你稍等一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.71,0:12:09.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为你错了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.35,0:12:12.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然用钩索
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.22,0:12:14.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在 红月君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:15.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.52,0:12:25.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 到调教时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.42,0:12:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪的战斗机 不过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.91,0:12:32.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Knightmare？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.61,0:12:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 之后拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.99,0:12:40.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下敌机4架
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.34,0:12:43.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连圆桌骑士也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:45.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下我的评价就会…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.23,0:12:46.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.29,0:12:48.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右翼护卫舰 无法操舵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.21,0:12:51.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去会撞上本舰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.30,0:12:52.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改变线路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.64,0:12:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来不及 即将冲撞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.95,0:13:06.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是老样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.42,0:13:07.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mordred的作风
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:10.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尼娅 别用那个了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.70,0:13:12.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了总督可怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.24,0:13:14.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是保护
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.61,0:13:18.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗伊德先生 Lancelot呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.32,0:13:21.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好了哦 快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.72,0:13:24.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将军 您要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.69,0:13:27.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去会被降职的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.58,0:13:29.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要亲手建立功勋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.83,0:13:31.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把黑色骑士团…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.50,0:13:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢货 竟把自己的引擎…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.28,0:13:45.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 ZERO就在我面前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.69,0:13:50.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 请给我勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:53.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,错的是布里塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.64,0:13:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇帝认为力量才是绝对的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.42,0:13:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也赞同这点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.75,0:14:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.32,0:14:04.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉总督 你只是被利用了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.37,0:14:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说眼和腿都不便的我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.86,0:14:09.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会引起大家的同情？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:10.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.91,0:14:14.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我自己的期望
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.48,0:14:18.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.15,0:14:21.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fsp-1}可能是因为ECCM（电子反干扰装置）的影响联络不上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.69,0:14:23.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本想和后方的千叶 红月合流
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:25.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探索舰内…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这艘舰即将坠落
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.35,0:14:29.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.88,0:14:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仙波
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.56,0:14:35.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我不喜欢欺凌弱小
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种…地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.47,0:14:39.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仙波！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.08,0:14:40.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤堂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:44.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陆战兵器奇袭可不像你的战术啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.04,0:14:47.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的期望？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.13,0:14:52.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为世界能够以更和平更温柔的方式改变
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:55.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我要继承尤菲皇姐的遗志
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.13,0:14:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次让日本行政特区…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.18,0:14:59.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,复活？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.10,0:15:04.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO 你也能加入吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.09,0:15:09.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人是能够改过自新的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.63,0:15:14.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO来抢夺娜娜莉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.71,0:15:17.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 机情没有发来报告
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人是ZERO 还是鲁路修？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.75,0:15:22.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枢木卿 现在确认情况
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.99,0:15:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉总督所乘坐的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.85,0:15:26.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2号浮空装置处于停止状态
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.66,0:15:28.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3号4号浮空装置相互联动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:30.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Caseθ发生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.89,0:15:36.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说明白点就是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.44,0:15:39.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去大家都要去洗海水浴了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.23,0:15:42.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿普森将军战死的报告也送来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.52,0:15:46.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在以救出总督最为优先
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.21,0:15:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轮椅信号 探索开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.93,0:15:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ECM（电子干扰装置）所产生噪音 清除开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.82,0:15:55.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预置阶段设定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.16,0:15:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先行发送舰内配置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.08,0:15:59.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数据链接 确认
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.17,0:15:59.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.04,0:16:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认总督现在位置后请发信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.97,0:16:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,频道MB 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.92,0:16:08.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lancelot Conquista 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.44,0:16:09.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.41,0:16:24.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲 我必须救出娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.34,0:16:26.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.65,0:16:29.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不求你原谅了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.42,0:16:31.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快躲起来 红月
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:32.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进入舰内的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:34.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 要等大家都逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:39.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.97,0:16:42.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红月
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.21,0:16:47.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快拉逃脱控制杆 红月
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.51,0:16:52.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整备不良？这种时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:16:57.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躲猫猫 结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.29,0:17:08.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会掉下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.83,0:17:10.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 红莲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.89,0:17:14.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.88,0:17:18.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最佳位置嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.20,0:17:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉克夏塔小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.49,0:17:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了 黑色骑士团特制的滑翔翼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.20,0:17:26.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,课本预习过了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.74,0:17:27.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.29,0:17:30.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就来正式的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.50,0:17:32.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本诱导交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.05,0:17:34.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦你救出ZERO大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.56,0:17:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.65,0:17:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三号垂直发射管 开放
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:41.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与红莲二式本体连接信号 确认
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.92,0:17:44.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞舞吧 滑翔翼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.26,0:17:47.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回转
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.22,0:17:53.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诱导信号 确认
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.72,0:17:55.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同步轴 顺利捕捉目标
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.39,0:17:56.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连接
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.54,0:17:57.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连接
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.20,0:18:03.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.72,0:18:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续 穿甲炮击右腕部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.88,0:18:12.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右腕部 减速至连接速度
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.72,0:18:15.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传送神经元 0.5到0.8MMP
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.93,0:18:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无障碍感
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.25,0:18:20.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第1至第5屈伸肌 正常运作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.84,0:18:23.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冲击控制 确认启动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.22,0:18:24.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以连接
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.58,0:18:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.44,0:18:35.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管他有多少敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.16,0:18:41.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我队追击藤堂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.74,0:18:43.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 这边去将总督…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.80,0:18:45.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往空中来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.99,0:18:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色骑士团也有浮空装置
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.15,0:18:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红月君 ZERO就…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.72,0:18:50.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定救他出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.19,0:18:54.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 获得浮空能力和护盾了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:18:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.10,0:18:58.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若这红莲都不通用就彻底完了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.96,0:19:00.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也只能放手一搏了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.99,0:19:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轰他一炮试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.19,0:19:03.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.34,0:19:10.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远距离？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.00,0:19:15.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.01,0:19:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有这红莲可翔式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.21,0:19:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀 你去救总督
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.96,0:19:21.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别大意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.95,0:19:24.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方可是赢过杰里米亚卿的机师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.89,0:19:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只橘子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.34,0:19:28.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.34,0:19:34.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 圆桌骑士水准？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.90,0:19:36.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 这样就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.57,0:19:41.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别小看红莲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:44.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脏脚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.03,0:19:49.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们靠后站
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.26,0:19:56.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连广域攻击都有？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.06,0:19:58.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能源总量呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.35,0:19:59.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是将能量扩散开而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.24,0:20:03.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 看机体损伤恐怕暂时难以动弹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.17,0:20:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那架Knightmare是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.94,0:20:08.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 强的是机师吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.37,0:20:10.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本该认真点的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲 在这情势下还要攻来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.10,0:20:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成 ZERO在旗舰内
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.54,0:20:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.71,0:20:21.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招吧 丰饶女神之网（Gefion Net）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.80,0:20:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个我早有对策
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.37,0:20:32.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你也被绊住了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.24,0:20:36.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.55,0:20:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界树引擎（Yggdrasill Drive）的能量明明已经提高了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.64,0:20:40.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.00,0:20:42.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查明总督的现在位置了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.19,0:20:45.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主舰桥后方的庭园空间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.59,0:20:47.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是离坠落只有47秒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.99,0:20:48.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定救出她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.28,0:20:50.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.01,0:20:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲 现在别理朱雀了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.60,0:20:57.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快救ZERO大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.55,0:20:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 但是在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.64,0:21:01.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.95,0:21:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用核心光锥（Core Luminous Cone）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.57,0:21:09.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Go
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.63,0:21:15.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.31,0:21:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能暴露ZERO的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.30,0:21:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是强行带走她的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.97,0:21:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就等同扭曲娜娜莉的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.77,0:21:26.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.54,0:21:29.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跟我逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.01,0:21:30.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.52,0:21:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.57,0:21:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 他是将我卖给皇帝的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.10,0:21:38.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.88,0:21:42.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受惊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.95,0:21:44.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.59,0:21:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉 和朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.12,0:21:53.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO 这次暂且…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.41,0:22:03.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1200)}娜娜莉！
